# Test your FastAPI endpoints

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/
Accept: application/json

###

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health
Accept: application/json

###

POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/chat/clear
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_id": "demo-session"
}

###

POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/chat/sync
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "你好，帮我查看系统状态",
  "session_id": "demo-session"
}

###

# 测试触发工具调用：获取所有设备
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/chat/sync
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "列出所有设备",
  "session_id": "demo-session"
}

###

# 测试触发工具调用：获取指定检测点的设备
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/chat/sync
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "查看检测点1的所有设备",
  "session_id": "demo-session"
}

###

# 测试会话记忆：继续对话
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/chat/sync
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "这些设备中第一个是什么",
  "session_id": "demo-session"
}
